782693515", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/clu/136/goblin-wizardry?utm_source=api", "local": "img/wizard/f621dcaa-c500-4a17-a65a-60d9b5516a3b.jpg"}, {"id": "29ef75e2-e3c9-4491-8345-b40ff39caadd", "name": "The Unknown Wizard", "set": "UNK", "set_name": "Unknown Event", "released": "2024-10-25", "type_line": "Legendary Creature — Human Wizard", "rarity": "mythic", "colors": ["B", "G", "R", "U", "W"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/a/0/a0af46f8-5abf-4436-9bb4-906ad44420d6.jpg?1782727585", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/a/0/a0af46f8-5abf-4436-9bb4-906ad44420d6.jpg?1782727585", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/unk/MZ01/the-unknown-wizard?utm_source=api", "local": "img/wizard/29ef75e2-e3c9-4491-8345-b40ff39caadd.jpg"}, {"id": "7d4b6613-9000-4f53-9737-fe0338f3f629", "name": "Erudite Wizard", "set": "FDN", "set_name": "Foundations", "released": "2024-11-15", "type_line": "Creature — Human Wizard", "rarity": "common", "colors": ["U"], "img_small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/9/2/9273c417-0fcd-4273-b24e-afff76336d0c.jpg?1782689234", "img_normal": "https://cards.scryfall.io/normal/front/9/2/9273c417-0fcd-4273-b24e-afff76336d0c.jpg?1782689234", "scryfall_uri": "https://scryfall.com/card/fdn/37/erudite-wizard?utm_source=api", "local": "img/wizard/7d4b6613-9000-4f53-9737-fe0338f3f629.jpg"}], "flavor_snippets": [{"card": "Patchwork Gnomes", "set": "MH2", "html": "One <mark>wizard</mark>&#x27;s trash is another <mark>wizard</mark>&#x27;s roving gang of abominations.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/0/3002ccef-5322-4f99-9fce-3b4303347240.jpg?1782704560"}, {"card": "Angelic Shield", "set": "DDI", "html": "&quot;If only an angel&#x27;s wings could shelter us all.&quot;\n—Barrin, master <mark>wizard</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/b/5/b5c268cc-891b-49df-8964-736d325b9403.jpg?1782752382"}, {"card": "Sideswipe", "set": "CHK", "html": "Hisoka&#x27;s <mark>wizards</mark> struggled for years to master the art of redirection that came so naturally to the shamans of Ganzan Pass.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/6/b/6bd611b7-7bd3-4a76-bd69-34a7235965ae.jpg?1782718182"}, {"card": "Brightstone Ritual", "set": "ONS", "html": "<mark>Wizards</mark> fought over the stone to exploit its power. Goblins fight over it because it&#x27;s shiny.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/b/5b08b0a6-c94e-4407-8a24-c8202497b5f2.jpg?1782719137"}, {"card": "Dark Banishing", "set": "TPR", "html": "&quot;It is the way of most <mark>wizards</mark> to begin by exiling themselves and to end by exiling everyone else.&quot;\n—Hanna, *Weatherlight* navigator", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/4/141dbd31-b813-46da-849e-e13d97dd2e17.jpg?1782750722"}, {"card": "Zzzyxas's Abyss", "set": "UNH", "html": "Tired of always being picked last, the <mark>wizard</mark> Zzzyxas created the ultimate revenge.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/d/1/d1ead203-b976-46d7-81c7-86ada091a4ec.jpg?1782754095"}, {"card": "Owlbear", "set": "AFR", "html": "Many people believe a misguided <mark>wizard</mark> created the first owlbear, but others insist that these creatures have always dwelled in the Feywild.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/3/0/30e8a00f-8131-470d-8072-4c23b812281a.jpg?1782704325"}, {"card": "Vertigo", "set": "6ED", "html": "&quot;I saw the <mark>wizard</mark> gesturing, but I didn&#x27;t guess his plan until my aesthir cried out and went into a dive.&quot;\n—Arna Kennerüd, skyknight", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/0/a/0a58ac6a-095e-47d7-ba42-56d148e3c6b9.jpg?1782720463"}, {"card": "Preposterous Proportions", "set": "FDN", "html": "Their acorn hunt was unsuccessful, but they did find the <mark>wizard</mark>&#x27;s experimental potion cache.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/c/acb65189-60e4-42e0-9fb1-da6b716b91d7.jpg?1782689171"}, {"card": "Clockwork Gnomes", "set": "ME4", "html": "&quot;Until I came to the Floating Isle, I never had to oil the servants.&quot;\n—Baki, <mark>wizard</mark> attendant", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/f/7/f74a8952-fad0-40c3-88eb-3cc05acaf590.jpg?1782752694"}, {"card": "Diabolical Salvation", "set": "PH17", "html": "To succeed, the <mark>wizards</mark> made a deal with devils.", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/8/0/8007e300-d16c-4257-9a93-4c82750414fe.jpg?1782747486"}, {"card": "Irini Sengir", "set": "HML", "html": "&quot;That cruel being brings shame to all her fellow Dwarves and misery to all the land. She is Sengir&#x27;s daughter in spirit if not in blood.&quot;\n—Reveka, <mark>Wizard</mark> Savant", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/5/1/518e3b77-d482-4b90-94c0-0b8cdd949b9f.jpg?1782721579"}, {"card": "Psychic Spear", "set": "BOK", "html": "&quot;The <mark>wizards</mark> of Takenuma Swamp faced the horrors of humanity every day. It&#x27;s no wonder they fared so well against the kami.&quot;\n—*Observations of the Kami War*", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/c/1c2f024b-e77e-426b-930e-85b87e046f9b.jpg?1782718101"}, {"card": "Splash Portal", "set": "BLB", "html": "&quot;Don&#x27;t ask me how it works. If I stopped long enough to question it, I&#x27;d lose my legs.&quot;\n—Lorb, frogfolk <mark>wizard</mark>", "art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/a/d/adbaa356-28ba-487f-930a-a957d9960ab0.jpg?1782690577"}], "mechanics_snippets": [{"card": "Summon the School", "set": "LRW", "html": "Create two 1/1 blue Merfolk <mark>Wizard</mark> creature tokens.\nTap four untapped Merfolk you control: Return this card from your graveyard to your hand."}, {"card": "Giant's Amulet", "set": "KHM", "html": "When this Equipment enters, you may pay {3}{U}. If you do, create a 4/4 blue Giant <mark>Wizard</mark> creature token, then attach this Equipment to it."}, {"card": "Queen Brahne", "set": "FIN", "html": "Whenever Queen Brahne attacks, create a 0/1 black <mark>Wizard</mark> creature token with &quot;Whenever you cast a noncreature spell, this token deals 1 damage to each opponent.&quot;"}, {"card": "Acquisitions Expert", "set": "ZNR", "html": "When this creature enters, target opponent reveals a number of cards from their hand equal to the number of creatures in your party. You choose one of those cards. That player discards that card. (Your party consists of up to one each of Cleric, Rogue, Warrior, and <mark>Wizard</mark>.)"}, {"card": "Cascade Seer", "set": "ZNR", "html": "When this creature enters, scry X, where X is the number of creatures in your party. (Your party consists of up to one each of Cleric, Rogue, Warrior, and <mark>Wizard</mark>.)"}, {"card": "Kaza, Roil Chaser", "set": "OTC", "html": "Flying, haste\n{T}: The next instant or sorcery spell you cast this turn costs {X} less to cast, where X is the number of <mark>Wizards</mark> you control as this ability resolves."}, {"card": "Summon: Esper Ramuh", "set": "FIN", "html": "II, III — <mark>Wizards</mark> you control get +1/+0 until end of turn."}, {"card": "Deadly Alliance", "set": "ZNR", "html": "This spell costs {1} less to cast for each creature in your party. (Your party consists of up to one each of Cleric, Rogue, Warrior, and <mark>Wizard</mark>.)\nDestroy target creature or planeswalker."}], "thumb": {"art": "https://cards.scryfall.io/art_crop/front/1/3/13a4c124-216b-44b1-b49a-3db3f033e4cd.jpg?1782716384", "small": "https://cards.scryfall.io/small/front/1/3/13a4c124-216b-44b1-b49a-3db3f033e4cd.jpg?1782716384", "card": "Summon the School"}}